name: bún thịt nướng
description: [001] Bún thịt nướng is a rice noodle dish from Vietnam, served warm with grilled pork ribs and plenty of herbs. /// the circle of food by moth1 is a series of photographs of popular dishes from southeast Asia, digitally mirrored to form a geometric image, and then split into layers to create a parallax effect. 1000px, 15s mp4 looping video.
